{"tid":711320,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"罷搭港鐵，只搭巴士","createTime":"2018-06-21T12:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T09:59:24.000Z","uid":108894,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e01ae1784599e8ed52044edbd9de73a14939d1e9","tid":711320,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"邊個再搭港鐵就係變相容忍港鐵工程做假，隱瞞真相，置市民生命安全不顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個真心對港鐵感到憤怒嘅，理應善用巴士，罷搭港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港鐵我屌你老母</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b099ceb45f943c6c358fa5026035f5d037222a9","tid":711320,"uid":61271,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:24:19.000Z","msg":"大埔公路的嚴重九巴車禍，再次掀起社會關注車長工時長的問題。一批月薪車長不滿「被代表」接收資方提出的改善薪酬架構方案，決定晚上8時發動工業行動抗議。惟有9A狀元車長之稱、現為九巴董事總經理辦公室行政助理梁領彥（Gary），下午在個人facebook帳戶發帖，不點名批評罷駛司機「發死人財」太過份。不少網民不齒梁領彥為高層護航，轟梁是走狗、「屁股決定腦袋，9A也是不過如此」，自製公關災難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180224/57871287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F57871287&d=whoAJaSLdZX72J61Z%2FbMTW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e098e511\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F57871287&h=5c793c9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180224/57871287</a>"},{"pid":"ddc59890a1d1ca0bd78b076e6e11bf1c0a7f6145","tid":711320,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"無可能"},{"pid":"2872d1945